---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Layanan | Ekosistem Solusi">
<main class="pt-32 pb-20">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-12 mb-24 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-container/30 border border-outline-variant/15 rounded-full text-primary-fixed-dim text-xs font-label tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed-dim animate-pulse"></span>
Ekosistem Solusi
</div>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-bold leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter md: font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                    Merancang <br/><span class="text-primary-fixed-dim">Kecerdasan.</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-lg leading-relaxed font-body">
                    Kami menjembatani kesenjangan antara data mentah dengan strategi siap tindak lanjut melalui integrasi sistem kinetik dan otomatisasi.
                </p>
</div>
<div class="relative h-[400px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden glass-panel border border-outline-variant/15">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60" data-alt="Abstract 3D digital landscape with glowing cyan nodes and data streams interconnected in a dark space, cinematic lighting" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDmM6HVat5qGZX41MV7RxiJY6zufHP6RV-MHHUq9-8FX-3jnm9OrFh27zodgzdfogLCQlkc-FOuYdDub1lk0Vl5katOBhf1jHh_sU1HkHdJMcfBu0r1L_4k6gDY_1JTY9OOvNr0To2GzYwa9Hj1g0RQcW4xcZ5HDYo61BX8JJAKwLtSsGLW1r1v8HcwREQaYX-EVBsDIH0P0DGSPtwaPATWwra5tmAnOV-hgKy4SRUVVet5ZNg7l5VxLg05r8izNWZ6-ep4JQArZZVT"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface to-transparent"></div>
</div>
</header>
<!-- Main Services Grid -->
<section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-12 space-y-32">
<!-- AI & Automation -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
<div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl" data-icon="auto_awesome" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">auto_awesome</span>
<h2 class="text-3xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">AI &amp; Otomatisasi</h2>
</div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body">Alur kerja kognitif yang berevolusi dengan tujuan bisnis Anda, mengurangi gesekan manual dalam pekerjaan hingga 90%.</p>
</div>
<div class="lg:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="relative p-8 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low hover:bg-surface-container transition-all group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-4" data-icon="account_tree">account_tree</span>
<h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Otomatisasi Alur Kerja</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Hilangkan tugas manual berulang dengan menggunakan logika pemrograman berbantu robot yang cerdas.</p>
</div>
<div class="relative p-8 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low hover:bg-surface-container transition-all group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-4" data-icon="smart_toy">smart_toy</span>
<h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Chatbot AI</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Antarmuka pemrosesan bahasa alami (NLP) ramah pelanggan untuk bantuan non-stop 24/7 dan dukungan internal tim perusahaan.</p>
</div>
<div class="relative p-8 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low hover:bg-surface-container transition-all group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-4" data-icon="description">description</span>
<h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Pemrosesan Dokumen</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Ekstraksi dokumen kertas & pengkasifikasian format data otomatis dari lampiran PDF tidak terstruktur.</p>
</div>
<div class="relative p-8 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low hover:bg-surface-container transition-all group border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-4" data-icon="troubleshoot">troubleshoot</span>
<h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Dukungan Keputusan Eksekutif</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Mesin layanan sistem analitik prediktif kompleks yang mememberikan sinyal rekomendasi keputusan operasional penting.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- System Integration (Bento Style) -->
<div class="space-y-12">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end gap-6 border-b border-outline-variant/15 pb-8">
<div class="space-y-2">
<h2 class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Integrasi Sistem</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body">Mensinergikan platform yang berbeda ke dalam titik ekosistem kinetik terpusat tunggal.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<span class="px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest font-label">Siap Untuk Perusahaan</span>
<span class="px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest font-label">Sinkronisasi Real-Time</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 grid-rows-2 gap-4 h-auto md:h-[500px]">
<div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-10 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-5xl mb-6" data-icon="hub">hub</span>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Pengembangan &amp; Manajemen API</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-xs font-body">Middleware kustom dan jaringan REST/GraphQL yang kuat dirancang khusus untuk memenuhi standar skalabilitas serta keamanan tingkat maksimal.</p>
</div>
<img class="absolute bottom-[-20%] right-[-10%] w-2/3 opacity-20 rotate-12 pointer-events-none filter drop-shadow-2xl" data-alt="Close up of a high-tech server room with glowing blue LED indicator lights and fiber optic cables" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCxno0C57o6M7YUjb5dppL0_c2XNL9Dg718WoTg-c31sHzXyzxHGTfu_vBdpuIZRgb2X53ALWpcFQXNOE_CWg0_tPGorkOkShiydqrsd2zeyzGeG6BOug06VCqc0pqFagFyp1nEUAPZDpSSJkJXFuL_wyxLM5u0L5Q-qIzGU1S2AMYK99S-D3F3ODs6soA01PNDX6Yv2JiLytVbSBl3ykjyIxt26MJDf2I1nD770OeXFTiI36Onlzy5-nN9Jsrw8r3lKdizm-r_mplf"/>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-2 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-8 flex items-center gap-8 border-l-4 border-primary-fixed-dim border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="space-y-2">
<h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Integrasi ERP &amp; CRM</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Sinkronisasi lingkungan Salesforce, SAP, dan Oracle ke dalam sistem manajemen inti pusat.</p>
</div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl opacity-50" data-icon="sync_alt">sync_alt</span>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-2 bg-surface-container-high rounded-lg p-8 flex flex-col justify-center border border-outline-variant/10">
<h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Sinkronisasi Data</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Protokol sinkronisasi bolak-balik dengan latensi sangat rendah untuk kelancaran ekosistem.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Infrastructure & Software (Side-by-Side) -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
<!-- Digital Infrastructure -->
<div class="space-y-8 p-10 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-primary opacity-10" data-icon="cloud">cloud</span>
</div>
<h2 class="text-3xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white border-l-2 border-primary pl-6">Infrastruktur Digital</h2>
<ul class="space-y-6">
<li class="flex gap-4 group">
<span class="text-primary-fixed-dim font-headline font-bold border-b border-primary/20 leading-none h-fit">01</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-headline">Migrasi Cloud &amp; Strategi</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Transisi lancar ke ekosistem AWS, Azure, atau platform GCP dengan rasio perbandingan harga yang lebih rendah.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex gap-4 group">
<span class="text-primary-fixed-dim font-headline font-bold border-b border-primary/20 leading-none h-fit">02</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-headline">Siklus Kehidupan DevOps &amp; CI/CD</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Mengotomatisasi perizinan jalan sistem tanpa harus mengganggu ekosistem perangkat lunak.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex gap-4 group">
<span class="text-primary-fixed-dim font-headline font-bold border-b border-primary/20 leading-none h-fit">03</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-headline">Arsitektur Layanan Mikro</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Memisahkan sistem monolitik agar menjadi komponen microservices yang ringkas tanpa gangguan komunal.</p>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<!-- Software Development -->
<div class="space-y-8 p-10 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-primary opacity-10" data-icon="terminal">terminal</span>
</div>
<h2 class="text-3xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white border-l-2 border-primary-fixed-dim pl-6">Pengembangan Perangkat Lunak</h2>
<ul class="space-y-6">
<li class="flex gap-4 group">
<span class="text-primary font-headline font-bold border-b border-primary/20 leading-none h-fit">01</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-headline">Sistem SaaS Perusahaan</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Pengembangan Perangkat Lunak kustom menggunakan kerangka arsitektur teraman tingkat komersial.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex gap-4 group">
<span class="text-primary font-headline font-bold border-b border-primary/20 leading-none h-fit">02</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-headline">Aplikasi Web Berkinerja Tinggi</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Pembangunan perangkat lunak untuk lingkungan web interaktif multi platform dengan performa tercepat di kelasnya.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex gap-4 group">
<span class="text-primary font-headline font-bold border-b border-primary/20 leading-none h-fit">03</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-headline">Sistem Tertanam (IoT)</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Pengembangan firmware hardware kustom dari Raspberry Pi hingga sensor otomatisasi tingkat lanjut.</p>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<!-- IT Consulting (Editorial Layout) -->
<div class="relative bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-12 lg:p-24 border border-outline-variant/15 overflow-hidden">
<div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
<div class="space-y-8">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary/10 px-4 py-1 rounded-full">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"></span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary tracking-widest uppercase font-label">Nasihat Sistematis</span>
</div>
<h2 class="text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-none">Modernisasi <br/>Strategis.</h2>
<p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">
                            Kami tidak hanya membangun infrastruktur; Kami menganalisis arsitektur sistem anda dan menentukan jalur untuk meningkatkan eskalasi performa Anda.
                        </p>
<button class="bg-surface-container-highest text-slate-900 dark:text-white border border-primary/20 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-headline font-semibold hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all">
                            Lihat Metodologi Audit
                        </button>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-2 border-primary-fixed-dim hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors border border-outline-variant/15">
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2 font-headline">Strategi Transformasi Digital</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Peta jalan untuk mendorong pergerakan skala sistem konvensional lama ke kerangka terintegrasi cerdas terbaru yang mulus.</p>
</div>
<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-2 border-primary-fixed-dim hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors border border-outline-variant/15">
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2 font-headline">Rekomendasi Tumpukan Teknologi</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Penyelekisan kerangka kerja mana yang paling menjanjikan pengembalian modal IT tercepat untuk perusahaan dan korporat Anda.</p>
</div>
<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-2 border-primary-fixed-dim hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors border border-outline-variant/15">
<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2 font-headline">Penilaian Peluang Otomatisasi Tersembunyi</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Mengkuantifikasi persentase target peningkatan bisnis (ROI) pada investasi otomatisasi Anda bahkan sebelum perancangan purwarupa (prototype).</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Decorative element -->
<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-1/2 opacity-20 pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-tl from-primary-fixed-dim to-transparent blur-3xl"></div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

<style>
.tonal-transition {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #10141a, transparent);
}
.glass-panel {
    background: rgba(28, 32, 38, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
}
.node-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    background-color: #4cd6ff;
}
.signature-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4cd6ff 0%, #006178 100%);
}
</style>
</BaseLayout>
